{"tid":1544454,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一句睇現今愛情","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:22:09.000Z","uid":318637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d4e2bf194a5298fe7eef9a087544d0f169d3fc47","tid":1544454,"uid":318637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"其實偷食出軌係咪好正常嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dc4d14dd20e066052c81f9de7358dbd50ae5e7","tid":1544454,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e91jFMP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe91jFMP.gif&h=6056e7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日<br />\n絕對和理非<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n12:00pm <br />\n遮打集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm<br />\n<ins>美國駐港澳總領事館</ins> <br />\n為《香港人權及民主法案》請願</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽熟首歌未？<br />\n好撚好聽<br />\n到時一齊唱 ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\nOh, say can you see,<br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed,<br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=2c27191e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揮國旗(<span style=\"color: blue;\">美國</span>x<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>) ：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CAXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"56cb95a8df53a9f5b12741174e99e4422754c07d","tid":1544454,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"737df19c9330fe474e6dc2c605f8c904ecfd0d3c","tid":1544454,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56cb95a8df53a9f5b12741174e99e4422754c07d","tid":1544454,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4e2bf194a5298fe7eef9a087544d0f169d3fc47","tid":1544454,"uid":318637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"其實偷食出軌係咪好正常嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:04:34.000Z","msg":"黑鏡第五季<br />\n<br />\n探討更多可能嘅伴侶關係"},{"pid":"b056b6323e43ce80dfc9d0d367ffe6ef38a7ce5d","tid":1544454,"uid":318637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"737df19c9330fe474e6dc2c605f8c904ecfd0d3c","tid":1544454,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56cb95a8df53a9f5b12741174e99e4422754c07d","tid":1544454,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4e2bf194a5298fe7eef9a087544d0f169d3fc47","tid":1544454,"uid":318637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:35:30.000Z","msg":"其實偷食出軌係咪好正常嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:04:34.000Z",